  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose a character that fits the situation</h2>Choose between 8 characters from four different classes. Each character has abilities and weapons that make them unique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/eddfb2c041ab487e3f5d1abaa68428a3.poster.avif?t=1764266170\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/eddfb2c041ab487e3f5d1abaa68428a3.webm?t=1764266170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/eddfb2c041ab487e3f5d1abaa68428a3.mp4?t=1764266170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play different game modes</h2>Go on expeditions in the city and get ready to face more than 10 different completely randomized game modes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/cc979fedfa6cc4b996f046c7300182b8.poster.avif?t=1764266170\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/cc979fedfa6cc4b996f046c7300182b8.webm?t=1764266170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/cc979fedfa6cc4b996f046c7300182b8.mp4?t=1764266170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your refuge to unlock new content</h2>Finishing an expedition will earn you supplies to upgrade your shelter and unlock new maps, character upgrades, and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/43582e770e6696d6370064ef27b0739d.poster.avif?t=1764266170\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/43582e770e6696d6370064ef27b0739d.webm?t=1764266170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268710/extras/43582e770e6696d6370064ef27b0739d.mp4?t=1764266170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
